Hi.
With the permission of Jozz (FluenZa_), I have decided to re-create the music thread that 1Theodore1 created a while back. The original thread is missing so here is the reboot!

Post your favourite music and share your playlist with the community!

Rules:
> No spam
> No inappropriate songs

Also, do not ridicule someone's playlist or songs because they are created by an artist you despise, etc. 

What I Recommend:
Changing. Come back from time to time.
